<voice_0x01001C37><se_low>It's Maurice.: See, I dreamed of finding a true warrior, a hero who would defeat me too.
<voice_0x01001C38><se_low>It's Maurice.: However, this is not the only objective of the Ninth Athletics.
<voice_0x01001C39><se_low>It's Maurice.: As an owner, my job is to control the heat and arousal.
<voice_0x01001C3A><se_low>It's Maurice.: So we invite you to take part in the competition. The day we met, I saw in your eyes that you brought my love as a blessing.
<voice_0x01001C3B><se_low>It's Maurice.: have you ever lied to me No, you do whatever I want.
<voice_0x01001C3C><se_low>It's Maurice.: But now Mr. Spatley wants more. The stronger the motivation, the stronger the passion.
<voice_0x01001C3D><se_low>It's Maurice.: Since this is Alola, I decided to find another fighter. Test Your New Abilities
<voice_0x01001C3E><se_low>It's Maurice.: Do you understand the AMI? We invite you to this new fight.
<voice_0x01001C3F><se_low>It's Maurice.: preparations are complete. Scene is set... Guard hidden... Hunt for treasure or ghost!
<voice_0x01001C41><se_low>It's Maurice.: All the fighters you will face are very strong and have the same abilities as you. Yes, there are important things ahead.

<party_order1_M_or_F_voice_0x01001C42><se_low><IF_MALE>It's Maurice.: Master, you have done a great job! Tell me what you're doing, alright?
